OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FEarly cloud will break to sunny
OL,6,Fspells, and with light and variable
OL,7,Fwinds it will be feeling warm. However
OL,8,Fcloud will thicken again from the
OL,9,Fnorthwest through the afternoon, and
OL,10,Fthe odd spot of rain cannot be ruled
OL,11,Fout.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FCloud breaking at times
OL,14,Fovernight, with clear spells allowing
OL,15,Fthe odd patch of mist and fog to
OL,16,Fdevelop. Perhaps staying cloudier
OL,17,Facross the Pennines, with the odd spot
OL,18,Fof rain.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
FL,167,160,301,260,100,100
PN,16602
